<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; color: #212529;">

  <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Hello <%= @resource.email %></h2>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    We received a request to reset your password. You can change your password by clicking the button below:
  </p>

  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="<%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %>"
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #0d6efd; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px;">
      Change My Password
    </a>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; line-height: 1.6;">
    If the button above doesn’t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; word-break: break-all; color: #343a40;">
    <%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    If you didn’t request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
    <br>Your password won’t change until you access the link above and set a new one.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 14px;">
    Thanks,<br>
    <strong>The Access Control App Team</strong>
  </p>

</div>
